{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"BroadcastChannel.name","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><em><code>name</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/postMessage\"><code>postMessage()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/messageerror_event\"><code>messageerror</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">読み取り専用の <strong><code>BroadcastChannel.name</code></strong> プロパティは、指定されたチャンネルをその名前で一意に識別する <a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> を返します。</span> この名前は作成時に <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/BroadcastChannel\" title=\"BroadcastChannel()\"><code>BroadcastChannel()</code></a> コンストラクタに渡されるため、読み取り専用です。</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>str</em> = <em>channe<code>l</code></em><code>.name;</code>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// チャンネルに接続</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">BroadcastChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'test_channel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// その他の操作（postMessage など）</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// チャンネル名をコンソールに記録します</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"test_channel\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 終了したら、チャンネルから切断します</span>\nbc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/comms.html#dom-broadcastchannel-name\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">BroadcastChannel.name の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.BroadcastChannel.name","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel\"><code>BroadcastChannel</code></a>: これが属するインターフェース。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"読み取り専用の BroadcastChannel.name プロパティは、指定されたチャンネルをその名前で一意に識別する DOMString を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BroadcastChannel.name","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"BroadcastChannel.name","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/broadcastchannel/name","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/broadcastchannel/name/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel","title":"BroadcastChannel"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BroadcastChannel/name","title":"BroadcastChannel.name"}],"pageTitle":"BroadcastChannel.name - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}